@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xtsbzp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos(v1))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.09) / wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.75)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.82) - (tmp * (v2 + 0.83 / v0 + 0.41)))
    data[tid] = v0
